ed-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/add-page-numbers-pdf\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">PDF Tools</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Add Page Numbers to PDF</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Add page numbers to each PDF page online for free.</p><span class=\"mt-auto pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a><a class=\"group flex min-h-56 flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/organize-pdf\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">PDF Tools</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Organize PDF</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Reorder and remove PDF pages online, then download an organized PDF.</p><span class=\"mt-auto pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a><a class=\"group flex min-h-56 flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/crop-pdf\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">PDF Tools</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Crop PDF</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Crop PDF page margins online by adjusting page crop boxes in your browser.</p><span class=\"mt-auto pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a></div></section><section class=\"px-6 pb-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl\"><aside class=\"rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 p-6\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase text-amber-200\">Sponsored</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-white\">Featured software partner</h3><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400\">A reserved placement for a relevant file, productivity or document software partner.</p><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-amber-200 hover:text-amber-100\" href=\"/partners\">Explore partnership options</a></aside></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-white/10 bg-slate-900/40 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black\">Why use these tools?</h2><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 leading-7 text-slate-300\">Complete common PDF workflows from one straightforward directory.</p><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 leading-7 text-slate-300\">Process documents client-side where possible with clear output limitations.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black\">Frequently asked questions</h2><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Can I merge and split PDFs here?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Yes. Dedicated tools support merging multiple PDFs and extracting selected page ranges.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Do PDF tools work with password-protected files?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Most tools require a standard unlocked PDF that the browser libraries can read.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Is PDF processing private?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">The listed PDF tools process documents in your browser rather than requiring a server upload.</p></div></div><h2 class=\"mt-16 text-2xl font-black\">Explore other categories</h2><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500